entries.femaleVariant: OK, bud, you've had your quota for the day.
Au contraire, my friend! Good sake's never done anybody any harm.
Japanese have this saying, see. First toast – man drinks the sake. Second toast – sake drinks the sake. Third toast – sake drinks the man.
Aww, runny bullshit, that. I got a better saying…
First toast – I get the sake. Second toast – you get the sake. Third toast – sake's on the house, yeah?
Tyger Claw bar, holmes. Ain't nothin' on the house here.
Tyger Claws...? Err... best be goin', yeah? Ah.
